Xinying, you know there's a girl

3
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:59,640
who got into a really amazing school

4
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:01,240
called Harvard.

5
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,520
When you grow up,

6
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,600
don't you want to go to Harvard?

7
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:09,919
Then we have to

8
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:11,120
train your willpower,

9
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:12,520
okay?

10
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:13,680
Do it with Mommy.

11
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,640
Hold out your hand.

12
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,400
Put an ice cube in it.

13
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:22,000
Yes, now squeeze.

14
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,079
That hand, squeeze it.

15
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:25,079
Count for yourself.

16
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:26,800
See how long you can last.

17
00:02:27,079 --> 00:02:27,520
One,

18
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:29,120
two,

19
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,000
three.

20
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,040
Tell yourself,

21
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:33,160
I'm not afraid,

22
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:34,960
